downloadTitle: MyAdvisor (formally Skype Operations Framework) Success Resources
downloadDescription: MyAdvisor (formally Skype Operations Framework) Success Resources
detailsSection: MyAdvisor (formally Skype Operations Framework) provides practical deployment guidance tailored towards ensuring your organization is setup for long-term operational success with Cloud Voice.
systemRequirementsSection:
• MyAdvisor Excel, PowerPoint and Word Success resources require either Office 2013 or Office 2016.
    • MyAdvisor PowerShell scripts require either PowerShell version 3 or version 4.
installInstructionSection:
• This download works with the following program:
    • Download the file by clicking the Download button and saving the file to your hard disk.
    • Extract the file to a hard disk location of your choosing.
  • To remove this download:
    • Delete the extracted folder and the downloaded .zip file.
